nodes.text: Star Wars: The Clone Wars Seasons 1-5 Collector's Edition

Star Wars: The Clone Wars Seasons 1-5 Collector's Edition is a fourteen-disc Blu-ray or nineteen-disc DVD boxed set of all five seasons of the Star Wars: The Clone Wars television series released on October 15, 2013. It includes The Art of Star Wars: The Clone Wars, a booklet with concept art from all five seasons.
